version_description:
What's New:
- The Ghost Face joins the playable Character roster
- Complete Daily Rituals to earn rewards
- New Exclusive Mask for the Trapper!
- 4 new maps added to Coldwind Farm: Torment Creek, Rancid Abattoir, The Thompson House and Fractured Cowshed
- Bug fixes and map lighting optimization implemented

What's new:
- Prestige is now available on Mobile! Prestige your max-level Characters to earn exclusive rewards
- In-game FAQ: Find all the answers to your questions without leaving the game using our support integration
- Introducing the Rank System to Mobile: climb your way up the rank ladder to test your skill
- Coldwind Farm's Rotten Fields map is now playable
- Fixed clipping and misplaced component issues with some customizations and weapons
- Fixed invisible collisions in multiple maps
- Fixed Tutorial localization issues
- Ritual generation optimization
- Assorted bug fixes and mobile optimization
